<h1>Pragmatic Swift - Issues 2017</h1>

<p>Reminder: this repo will be public and all the issues and discussions are going to be readable by everyone.</p>

<h3>Writing</h3>

<p>Checkout the current repo and use the correct pull request about your article.
Once the article is ready, move the card on the dedicated <a href="https://trello.com/b/3HGZJSkh/pragmatic-swift">Trello board</a> and let the editor/reviewer to read, fix typos and eventually give some suggestions in how to improve.</p>

<h3>Review</h3>

<p>While reviews, please comment on the PR directly on the line, so it&rsquo;s clear what the comment is about. If the comment is big or general, please use the PR as issue.</p>
